15/*! \file */
16
17#include <config.h>
18
19#include <isc/print.h>
20#include <isc/util.h>
21
22#include <dns/callbacks.h>
23#include <dns/log.h>
24
25static void
26stdio_error_warn_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *, const char *, ...)
27 ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 3);
28
29static void
30isclog_error_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks, const char *fmt, ...)
31 ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 3);
32
33static void
34isclog_warn_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks, const char *fmt, ...)
35 ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF(2, 3);
36
37/*
38 * Private
39 */
40
41static void
42stdio_error_warn_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks,
43 const char *fmt, ...)
44{
45 va_list ap;
46
47 UNUSED(callbacks);
48
49 va_start(ap, fmt);
50 vfprintf(stderr, fmt, ap);
51 va_end(ap);
52 fprintf(stderr, "\n");
53}
54
55static void
56isclog_error_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks, const char *fmt, ...) {
57 va_list ap;
58
59 UNUSED(callbacks);
60
61 va_start(ap, fmt);
62 isc_log_vwrite(dns_lctx, DNS_LOGCATEGORY_GENERAL,
63 DNS_LOGMODULE_MASTER, /* XXX */
64 ISC_LOG_ERROR, fmt, ap);
65 va_end(ap);
66}
67
68static void
69isclog_warn_callback(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks, const char *fmt, ...) {
70 va_list ap;
71
72 UNUSED(callbacks);
73
74 va_start(ap, fmt);
75
76 isc_log_vwrite(dns_lctx, DNS_LOGCATEGORY_GENERAL,
77 DNS_LOGMODULE_MASTER, /* XXX */
78 ISC_LOG_WARNING, fmt, ap);
79 va_end(ap);
80}
81
82static void
83dns_rdatacallbacks_initcommon(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks) {
84 REQUIRE(callbacks != NULL);
85
86 callbacks->magic = DNS_CALLBACK_MAGIC;
87 callbacks->add = NULL;
88 callbacks->rawdata = NULL;
89 callbacks->zone = NULL;
90 callbacks->add_private = NULL;
91 callbacks->error_private = NULL;
92 callbacks->warn_private = NULL;
93}
94
95/*
96 * Public.
97 */
98
99void
100dns_rdatacallbacks_init(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks) {
101 dns_rdatacallbacks_initcommon(callbacks);
102 callbacks->error = isclog_error_callback;
103 callbacks->warn = isclog_warn_callback;
104}
105
106void
107dns_rdatacallbacks_init_stdio(dns_rdatacallbacks_t *callbacks) {
108 dns_rdatacallbacks_initcommon(callbacks);
109 callbacks->error = stdio_error_warn_callback;
110 callbacks->warn = stdio_error_warn_callback;
111}
